{"tid":2171561,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【全民檢測】DNA一去不返！大律師提五大私隱危機：中資做檢測 市民零監察","createTime":"2020-08-24T04:40:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T04:46:11.000Z","uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1bcd9b81158227ee3cafaf8bc57de51265fe8006","tid":2171561,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T04:40:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200824/5WTXVZOFUNEZNFPZWNMCYPL2LE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200824%2F5WTXVZOFUNEZNFPZWNMCYPL2LE%2F&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzsmo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=ab37c8c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200824%2F5WTXVZOFUNEZNFPZWNMCYPL2LE%2F&h=1b6992ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200824/5WTXVZOFUNEZNFPZWNMCYPL2LE/</a><br />\n<br />\n政府力推的全民檢測，坊間質疑私隱外洩，本身為執業大律師的公民黨梁嘉善在Facebook撰文，提出全民檢測帶來的五大私隱外洩隱憂，包括檢測中資公司控制，市民無從監察運作；當局也可將收集得到的DNA，以「統計」等用途說成「檢測」一部份；最大問題更是無人知悉資料會否「被送中」。梁直指政府在抗疫問題上，處處盤算如何與北面接軌，「將抗疫問題『政治化』的，正正就是特區政府」。"},{"pid":"4b4c9b9c202f3c1f3c470258bbdefe40304f48a3","tid":2171561,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T04:40:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffd656ba6492035fc0ce85e9e121af6ce131b0f3","tid":2171561,"uid":200479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T04:42:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"976b26a9710c0ebf1e42af430e752599589284a8","tid":2171561,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b4c9b9c202f3c1f3c470258bbdefe40304f48a3","tid":2171561,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T04:40:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces